### Get all videos (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos

###

### Get videos with custom pagination
GET http://localhost:4000/api/videos?page=1&limit=10

###

### Filter by channel title
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos?channelTitle=Tech

###

### Filter by category ID (e.g., Science & Technology = 28)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos?categoryId=28

###

### Combined filters with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos?channelTitle=Gaming&categoryId=20&page=1&limit=30

###

### Test edge cases - page 2 with limit 5
GET http://localhost:3000/api/videos?page=2&limit=5
